des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in Auburn. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Auburn Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Auburn Vegan for a fact."
